Let $O$ be the center of the inscribed circle. Draw the altitude from $A$ to $\overline{OB}$, and call the foot of the altitude $D$. [asy]
import olympiad; import geometry; size(150); defaultpen(linewidth(0.8));
draw((sqrt(3),0)--origin--(0,1)--cycle);
